  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluation of the clinical results after total knee prosthesis, and correlation with the
      alignment of the lower limb.

      Radiological measurements by means of 3D technology will be performed. The clinical result
      will be stipulated by means of standardized questionnaires (KOOS, KSS and Oxford knee
      score-questionnaire).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
